{"tid":1205363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我呼籲大家，MTR一定唔會係12號當日搞","createTime":"2019-06-11T18:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T18:58:19.000Z","uid":59570,"like":61,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ce19d68c0ac6c38712fedc14d84b76c880332fb1","tid":1205363,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:20:30.000Z","msg":"話塞地鐵既聽一聽我講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我呼籲大家，MTR一定唔會係12號當日搞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為聽朝一早會有人出去港島support ，有d冇咁上心但有心既晏就訓醒都會去<br />\n<br />\n至於民陣既呼籲係放工即係下就至夜晚去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全日每段時間都需要交通工具運人去支援</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以聽日一定唔可以搞MTR</span><br />\n<br />\n要行動都最少過左聽日"},{"pid":"5c345a4fa18a34467df13394eb70862e303bf959","tid":1205363,"uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:20:45.000Z","msg":"推比多d人睇"},{"pid":"4e16fcc86ccb4c0c6dd7c6d5eedad536aabe4d50","tid":1205363,"uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:21:12.000Z","msg":"要享受地鐵既服務都要過左聽日先慢慢享受"},{"pid":"d8347a43eb851281a0adf1623f12f5f1c4758be8","tid":1205363,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:21:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2fe993b2d8e0afe6d13deaec2ccbb63ce7ab010","tid":1205363,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:21:26.000Z","msg":"手動頂置"},{"pid":"e92d07a0d518cf481ebc9f09d4be6b264e170e2c","tid":1205363,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:21:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01074d1191e7d4a006b82790257c3b4f8df7f1cb","tid":1205363,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:22:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34f410a78e5704938073127228610ba1c47c8f15","tid":1205363,"uid":175079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:22:59.000Z","ms